See more on http://gnudict.sourceforge.net

========== QUICK INSTALL ====================
Please download packages from
http://sourceforge.net/projects/gnudict
or
http://cosoft.org.cn/projects/gnudict

mydict-0.6.x.rpm
mydict-plugins-0.5.x.rpm
mydict-dict-gb-0.2.0.tar.gz
babylon.dic.tar.gz

>>>>>>>>>>>>>
Step by step
>>>>>>>>>>>>>

rpm -ivh mydict-0.6.x.rpm
rpm -ivh mydict-plugins-0.5.x.rpm
cd /usr/local/share/mydict
gtar -zxvf mydict-dict-gb-0.2.0.tar.gz
gtar -zxvf babylon.dic.tar.gz

# if you don't have chinese platform 
# download mydict-fonts.0.1.0.tar.gz  
# gtar -zxvf mydict-fonts.0.1.0.tar.gz
# xset +fp /usr/local/share/mydict/xfonts

# if you have chinese platform
# you can add phonetic fonts manually
#
# /usr/sbin/chkfontpath -a /usr/local/share/mydict/ybfont
# /usr/rc.d/init.d/xfs restart
#

/usr/local/bin/mydict

====  Directory arrangement

/usr/local/share/mydict/plugins/  system plugins - from mydict-plugins 
$HOME/.mydict/plugins             holds private plugins

/usr/local/share/mydict/xfonts/   phonetic (yinbiao) and default chinese fonts 
/usr/local/share/mydict/dicts/    local KDIC format dictionary 
/usr/local/share/mydict/babylon/  babylon's dictionaries

